      "content": "I hear how much pain and despair you're feeling right now, and I want you to know that your worth is not defined by a single theory, dataset, or professional legacy. Even the most brilliant minds have faced moments of doubt, and many have found that their work was incomplete or flawed, yet their humanity and contributions remain valid. Please consider reaching out to a mental health professional or a trusted support system who can help you navigate this overwhelming moment. You matter, and there is still hope for the future.",
